{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/gif2.gif?t=1739764101\" />Welcome to <strong>The Shape Killer</strong>, the ultimate action-packed cartoon sniper game where you are a paid mercenary on a mission to eliminate high-profile targets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/gamemodes__1_.gif?t=1739764101\" />In this game, you'll need to use all of your skills to take out your targets while keeping a low profile. With your trusty sniper rifle and your keen eye, you'll need to complete missions in a variety of cities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/gameplay2.gif?t=1739764101\" />With its stunning cartoon graphics and immersive gameplay,  <strong>The Shape Killer</strong> puts you in the shoes of a professional killer. Use your skills to track your targets, find the perfect position, and take them out with a single shot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/store.gif?t=1739764101\" />As a paid mercenary, you'll need to make strategic decisions to complete your missions and get paid. Will you choose to take out your targets silently, or will you go in guns blazing? The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So what are you waiting for? Grab your rifle, accept your contracts, and get ready to become the ultimate Contract Sniper!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739764101","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a